title: Uber wont go public for years CEO Travis Kalanick
text:
Uber won't go public for years: CEO Travis Kalanick 
Times Of India Thursday 22nd October, 2015 
Uber CEO Travis Kalanick expressed confidence in the firm's financial future and refrained from issuing defensive barbs against critics or competitors....
